default. 
defaultThe conclusions 
defaultof the report 
defaultare graded in terms of probability and confidence. 
defaultWe believe this provides a clear description of the robustness of the conclusions. 
defaultThe most robust conclusions are indicated by high levels 
defaulto
defaultf likelihood and/or confidence. Conversely the 
defaultleast robust 
defaultare assigned low likelihood/confidence.
